Package citadels

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIPlayer  
    App
    Entry point for the Citadels game.
    AppTest
    Test cases for district card parsing and districtDeck building.
    Board
    Tracks what districts each player has built in their city.
    CharacterCard
    Represents a character card in the game, which has a name, turn order, and a special ability description.
    CharacterDeck
    Represents the districtDeck of character cards used during the selection phase.
    Deck
    Represents the districtDeck of district cards used in the game.
    DistrictCard
    Represents a district card in the game.
    Game
    Represents the main game logic and state management for a session of Citadels.
    GameUtils
    Utility methods used throughout the Citadels game.
    HumanPlayer  
    InputHandler
    Handles user input and command processing during the game.
    Player
    Abstract base class representing a player in the Citadels game.
    PlayerScore
    Holds final score details for a player at the end of the game.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Game.Phase
    Represents the current phase of the game.
